Happy Passover! An abundant table. A warm gathering of family and friends. Raising our glasses to the future, always mindful of the past. Passover is a celebration of gratitude for life’s many gifts. How fortunate we are to share them at this very special time.

Apr 18, 2019 | 02:33 PM EDT DOUG KASS Acreage Holdings! * There is an enormous amount of late stage market advance "stuff" going on these days! Acreage, the subject of a Canopy Growth takeover traded as high as $30/share today. The shares are now $22.62/share.

Lots of smoke and mirrors out in this market - Acerage Holdings ($ACRGF) might be a good example. Its tough to figure out what's real and what's not - in a momentum based market. Thankfully the business media will ask the hard questions and will sort it out for all of us!
